TEXT(beginproblem());
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

$a = random(2,9,1);
$soln = $a * 2 / (5**(.5));

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));

Determine whether the integral is divergent or convergent. If it is convergent, evaluate it. If not, state your answer as "divergent."

$BR \[ \int_{2}^{\infty}  \frac{$a}{(x+3)^{3/2}} dx \]
$BR $BR \{ans_rule( 30) \}
$BR
EOT
ANS(num_cmp($soln));

